    you can connect I2C sensors for more intelligent functions. The 4-layer PCB design ensures stable signal transmission, making it more durable and reliable.
    This demo kit supports RESE switches, which allows you to freely choose different types of electronic ink screens and achieve more customized features.<br><br>
